---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';

const title = `Privacy Policy | ${SITE_TITLE}`;
const description = 'Read our Privacy Policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} theme="dark">
	<main class="flex-grow docs-site-container border-x">
		<article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
			<h1 class="heading-gold text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-8 leading-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="text-muted-foreground mb-12"><strong>Last Updated: March 26, 2026</strong></p>

			<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
			<p>
				Welcome to Hustle Teacher ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy
				Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.
			</p>

			<h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
			<h3>2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Contact Forms:</strong> Name, email, message content</li>
				<li><strong>Email Subscriptions:</strong> Email address (collected via MailerLite)</li>
				<li><strong>Comments:</strong> Name, email, comment text</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>IP address and browser information</li>
				<li>Pages visited and time spent on site</li>
				<li>Referral sources</li>
				<li>Device type (mobile, desktop, tablet)</li>
				<li>Approximate location (country/city level)</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>2.3 Analytics & Heat Mapping</h3>
			<p>
				We use Google Analytics 4 and Microsoft Clarity to understand how users interact with our site. These tools
				collect anonymized data about user behavior.
			</p>

			<h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>To respond to your inquiries and provide customer support</li>
				<li>To send marketing emails (only if you subscribed)</li>
				<li>To improve our website and user experience</li>
				<li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
				<li>To detect and prevent fraud or abuse</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Contact Form Data:</strong> Deleted after 30 days unless requested otherwise</li>
				<li><strong>Email List:</strong> Retained until you unsubscribe</li>
				<li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> Retained for 14 months by default</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
			<p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>MailerLite:</strong> Email marketing platform - <a href="https://www.mailerlite.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
				<li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Website analytics - <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
				<li><strong>Microsoft Clarity:</strong> Heatmap analytics - <a href="https://clarity.microsoft.com/" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
				<li><strong>Vercel:</strong> Hosting provider - <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
				<li><strong>Google reCAPTCHA:</strong> Spam protection - <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a></li>
			</ul>

			<h2>6. GDPR & CCPA Compliance</h2>
			<h3>6.1 EU Visitors (GDPR)</h3>
			<p>If you're in the EU, you have the right to:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Access your personal data</li>
				<li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
				<li>Request deletion ("right to be forgotten")</li>
				<li>Opt-out of marketing emails anytime</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>6.2 California Residents (CCPA)</h3>
			<p>You have the right to:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Know what personal information is collected</li>
				<li>Know whether your personal information is sold or disclosed</li>
				<li>Say no to the sale or sharing of personal information</li>
				<li>Access and delete information</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>7. Cookies</h2>
			<p>
				Our site uses cookies for analytics and functionality. You can control cookies through your browser settings.
				By using our site, you consent to our use of cookies as described in our Cookie Policy.
			</p>

			<h2>8. Security</h2>
			<p>
				We implement industry-standard security measures (SSL/HTTPS, firewalls) to protect your information. However,
				no system is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.
			</p>

			<h2>9. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
			<p>You can:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Request a copy of your data</li>
				<li>Update or correct your information</li>
				<li>Request deletion of your data</li>
				<li>Unsubscribe from our email list anytime</li>
			</ul>
			<p>To exercise these rights, email us at <strong><a href="mailto:thehustleteacher@gmail.com">thehustleteacher@gmail.com</a></strong></p>

			<h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
			<p>
				If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
				<br />
				<strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:thehustleteacher@gmail.com">thehustleteacher@gmail.com</a>
				<br />
				<strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://hustle-teacher.vercel.app">https://hustle-teacher.vercel.app</a>
			</p>

			<h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
			<p>
				We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. We will notify you of significant changes by posting the new
				policy on our site and updating the "Last Updated" date.
			</p>
		</article>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>
